Ihi, drus i sɛan leɛwaṛ nsen, acḥal i sen-yewwi, acḥal ɣezzif, acḥal lqay, acḥal i sen-yeḥlel i waḍu, ur d-yețțili ț-țaɛekkumt ula i sin-nsent,
Imezdaɣ n temdint n Babilun yebna mkul amkan iwakken ad iɛebden Ṛebbi, wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
