Tilawin-nni i ten-ițheggin iman-nsen di lexla, anagar amkan anda sɛan leɛcuc d ṣṣdigen-nsen ;
Di leǧwahi-nni, tella yiwet n tqeḍɛit tameqqrant n yilfan i gkessen dinna.
