Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen, ur țțafen ara ayen n diri ara hedṛen fell-aneɣ yerna ad nneḥcamen.
Lmelk amezwaru yesmar taqbuct-is ɣef yisaffen d leɛwanṣer n ddunit. Leɛqeṛ n wayagi meṛṛa tella tezmert n Sidi Ṛebbi weḥd-es.
Ula d amkan n lḥekmat ț-țzemmar n igenwan, ikcef itent-id zdat txelqit meṛṛa, iɣleb-itent s lmut n Mmi-s ɣef wumidag, imi d nețța i tḥekkmeḍ kullec.
ț-țideț, lumuṛat-agi sselmaden leɛbada, annuz akk-d uɛețțeb n lǧețțat nneɣ, țbanen-d amakken d ayen yelhan, lameɛna d ayen ur nezmir ad iɛawen bunadem ad iṭṭef iman-is.
Tweṣṣa-ț acḥal meqqeṛ imenɣi, ɣef watmaten n temdint n Lquds meṛṛa ț-țagi i d-yusan si tmurt n Yahuda yellan ț-țmurt n Arimati iḥekkmen ɣef lɛeskeṛ-is ; msefhamen ad kksen meṛṛa fell-asen aṭas n yemdanen i gețțawin-ten ɣer nnger.
