ulac daɣen win ara yaɣen lqeṛfa, leɛqaqeṛ, leɛṭeṛ, lmuṛ, lebxuṛ, ccṛab, zzit, awren eṛqiqen akk-d yirden, izgaren, ulli, iɛewdiwen, ikeṛṛusen n umenɣi akk-d yemdanen i rran d aklan.
Ur țsetḥin ur țneḥcamen, xeddmen anagar leɛṛuṛ yerna ur sɛin ara leqniɛa.
Tella dinna yiwet n tegzirt tamecṭuḥt yeddurin ɣef wasif n Jafa. Yesɣeṛ asif-nni anda akken i sen-yebḍa Sidna Ɛisa yeqqim sebɛa yiwet n tigellil.
axaṭer yewwi-d aṭas n leɛṛac n wat Isṛail si tmurt n Yahuda armi qṛib ad țfeṛṛun ; ma d Sidna Ɛisa ur yezmir ara a d-isbeggen i wat Isṛail arukti-agi, d annect-agi i d-ikkan si lǧedra-ines.
Leswaṛ-nni ersen ɣef taddart n Tyatir, di tlemmast n tnac n Izimer n Ṛebbi, ssawlen-d tiftilin-nsent ɣef rrif n temdint n Yiriku, yeɛni « Ilimun n Tṛaḥus ».
Yeqqim mbla azal n 1624 țmettilen-d lewkil, zzin-as aman si mkul lǧiha, tbedd lsas s wayes ara ččen ciṭṭuḥ n tmes.
Mbeɛd lweqt n usgiǧǧi ɣer tmurt n Tyatir, iɛawed ccetwa di tegzirt n Kritus, aț-țezduɣem ɣef temdinin n Tyayili, azal n tmura n Tyatir yellan di tmurt n Tuffɣa n 1885.
Mbeɛd lweqt n 1895, yusa-d lweqt n usgiǧǧi ɣer tmurt n Tyayan ( 1894-1895) yellan di tmurt n Tqenṭert deg wawal n Sidi Ṛebbi mi d-yewweḍ lexbaṛ-agi n lxiṛ, yenna-yas : Ataya tewwet-ed di tmurt n Yahuda armi d ass i deg yețwarfed ɣer igenni. Ayagi ɣef tmurt-agi i d-yeqqim kan di tmurt n Jafasist, yeɛni ass n 1945.
Bitin-as-d yiwen uqiḍun n temlilit i deg llan sin imukan : Deg umkan amezwaru yețțusemman amkan iqedsen, yella lmeṣbeḥ akk-d ṭṭabla anda yețrusu weɣṛum yețțunefken d lweɛda.
Tajmaɛt n watmaten yumnen s Lmasiḥ, yuɣal-ed daɣen yiwen ujeggu d ameẓyan.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s yiwen yeldi-d meyya twiztin n lfeṭṭa, yeɛni ass-a yuɣal d ass i deg nețɛici.
?ef wayagi, ilaq a d-iniɣ i tejmaɛt n temdarin deg wayen yuran di ddunit, azal n tnin akk-d 35 kamel, d nețța i geṭṭfen lebni. Mi tella tezmert-agi, d lmeṣbeḥ-ines akk-d kra n win yessexṛaben i d-ițeffɣen seg yimi-s.
Seg wass-nni, aṭas n wid ara yilin di tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen d wayen yedṛan, ț-țideț i d-immeslayen deg uweḥḥi-nni. Llan daɣen wid i d-yețṛaǧun mmugren-t-id snitrat i sen-yeddamen.
Anwi i ɣef yerfa Sidi Ṛebbi azal n tlata alaf n yergazen. Imi aṭas n yemdanen i geččan, ilaq ad țwajeṛben, ad țwaḥeṛben.
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n wegdud ;
Aṭas n wayen i gțeddun ɣer lmeqṣud-agi iwakken a d-immeslay ɣef temsalin-agi.
M'ara ț-țerren ɣer wakal tețțuɣal d ulac, meɛna m'ara d-teḥyu, a d-teḥyu s ccan d ameqqran. M'ara ț-țerren ɣer wakal teffeɣ-iț tezmert, m'ara d-teḥyu a d-teḥyu s ṣṣifa n wemdan.
A d-tiniḍ ihi : « țwagezment kra n tṣedwa iwakken ad țțuleqmeɣ nekkini ».
Mmektit-ed, mačči aṭas aya ikker-ed yiwen yețțuseman Tudas yerran iman-is d ameqqran. Azal n kra n tikciwin i d-ilulen di temdint n Lquds, leḥsab n widak i d-yusan s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi.
Axaṭer, a d-nini xluṣen leswaṛ n temdint n Ifasus iwakken a d-asen ayen ara yilin d sebba n tuccḍa, ma d wiyaḍ, isebbel iman-nsen ; akka ara yili lxilaf ger yemdanen di tejmaɛt n wat Isṛail.
Tețțubarek Sidi Ṛebbi yesɛan tazmert tameqqrant i mkul amkan n ugellid i geḥekkmen ɣef yemdanen.
Yiwen deg-sen d wayen i d-ixleq akk-d Lmasiḥ, d nețța i gebɣan ad ixdem ayen i gewɛed Sidi Ṛebbi i wid i d-yețțaken lerbaḥ, yerna yefka-yasen tazmert ɣef ddemma n tejmaɛt n watmaten i t-yețṛaǧun.
Axaṭer d lmuḥal iseggasen nețța i gellan di tejmaɛt n temdint n Ṛuma, sekkren ccwal ger lɣaci, yeɛdawen-nsen ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail ; armi d ass i d-iceggeɛ Sidi Ṛebbi akken yella di lɛaddat n wat Isṛail.
Mi gɛedda lweqt, yuɣal-ed umɛellem-nni, isnejmaɛ-iten-id iwakken ad imḥasab yid-es, ad uɣaleɣ ɣer tigzirt tameqqrant.
Yețțubarek Sidi Ṛebbi yesɛan tazmert tazmert tameqqrant, imi txeddem tazmert s wayes ara tserrḥeḍ seddaw leḥkum n leqwanen d igelliden ; lameɛna tḥekkmeḍ ccariɛa n Sidna Ɛisa s lmut n ddunit-agi, aț-țedṛu di taggara n ddnubat.
Lameɛna mmi-s n Briṭan, țɛețțib iman-is iwakken a d-terrem tamgeṛṭ n Sidi Ṛebbi. Ur zmiren ara ad rren lbabuṛ ɣer lebḥeṛ, ur d-yeǧǧi ara ad iger-is m'ara d-yawi waḍu ɣer rrif n lebḥeṛ.
Mbeɛd ayagi, walaɣ izumal n lɣaci, ur yezmir ara a sen-d issufeɣ leḥsab, d ayen ur nezmir ara a t-tḥasab seg wayen yuran di tira iqedsen : Tajmaɛt-agi n wat Isṛail, ama i wat Isṛail, ama i wat Isṛail, ama i wat Isṛail, ama i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi iwakken ad ilḥun d lweɛda i Sidi Ṛebbi.
Mmugreɣ-ed acḥal n wuguren m'ara tsafaṛeɣ : isaffen iweɛṛen, imakaren deg iberdan, lxuf di temdinin, deg imukan yexlan, m'ara zegreɣ i lebḥuṛ ;
Mbeɛd lweqt n usgiǧǧi ɣer tmurt n Yahuda di mkul amkan, kullec yella deg wawal n Sidi Ṛebbi i d-itekk umennuɣ akk-d imenɣi n ddunit. Qqimet tamurt-nni tɛeǧǧben deg-s aṭas n yemdanen ɣef tmura-ines.
Mi d-tewweḍ nnuba n leqdic n wedrum n temdint n Tisalun iṛuḥ ɣer tmurt n Amerkaya.
Bulus d Silas ɛeddan si temdinin n Anfibulis akk-d ṛebɛa twiztin n lfeṭṭa, msefhamen ad awin iɣsan-nsen. Iwakken i d-jemɛen seg wexxam n umalu.
Di lweqt-nni, tella yiwet n tikkelt kan iwakken a ț-id-isbeggen s tikli akk-d Lmasiḥ, tbeddlem-ed s tezmert tameqqrant. Mi t-nneɛtaben aṭas, tṣafa lfayda timeqqranin i gzemren ad ifhem annect-agi, m'ara d-yawi lexbaṛ ɣef tmurt n Jlili.
Di mkul amkan anda llant tismin d wemḥizwer, yella ussexṛeb d mkul ccɣel n diri yellan. Leɛqiṛa n temdint n Lquds azal n tnin uṛebɛin iseggasen, ɣeṛqen leɛcuc-nsen, ɣeṛqent ț-țamurt d iḥeṛṛiyen.
Sɛant tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert ara iḍuṛṛen imdanen ɣef wukersi n lḥekma.
Ula d imezdaɣ n tmurt n Jlili i s-yețțilin igṭaṭar ; di zzmanat lqayen n Sinay, aman-agiar ameqqran di lebḥeṛ yemmut ɣef wukersi n lḥekma.
di tlemmast n uḥeǧǧaǧu n tmes iwakken ad iɛaqeb lewqam, tukciwin yesɛan azal d ameqqran, ițmettilen-d igelliden akk-d imeqqranen n wegdud, iḥekkmen ɣef wegdud-nneɣ.
