Lameɛna mmi-s n taklit-nni, ilul-ed ɣef weqṛaḥ n dayem i gețṛaǧun Aderɣal. Yefka lameṛ i gețțubarek win i d-yusan s tezmert n Sidi Ṛebbi ; itɛeǧǧeb deg-sen ɣef wedrar n tafat iwakken a ț-iɛaqeb Sidi Ṛebbi.
