Leḥjab yellan deg yiwet n tegzirt tamecṭuḥt yeddurin ɣef waḍu, isem-is Maṣeṛ, d yiwen seg idurar n tmurt-nni.
S tideț m'ara ɣ-țṛebbin yețɣiḍ aɣ lḥal lameɛna m'ara tɛeddi teswiɛt-nni, a naf belli d ayen yelhan i tudert-nneɣ.
Ur nezmir ara a nxiḍ tafaweț tajḍiṭ i uceṭṭiḍ aqdim, neɣ m'ulac tafaweț-nni ara s-nernu aț-țesseɣṛes aceṭṭiḍ-nni aqdim dɣa acerrig-nni ad innerni.
Leɛqed amezwaru yesɛa leqwanen yesɛan daɣen amkan anda ɛebbden Ṛebbi.
Lbabuṛ nni yewwi-d yiwen n leswaṛ n temdint n Lquds, yellan d azeggaɣ ɣlayen n mkul ṣṣenf. M'ara ɛeddin walef wegdud ! M'ara yexdem a t-id-yaweḍ tmezduɣt-nni iwakken ad ḥemden Sidi Ṛebbi a t-ɛebden.
sselɛa-nni n ddheb d lfeṭṭa, idɣaɣen ɣlayen d iɛeqcan, lkețțan n lfina akk-d lkețțan azeggaɣ d leḥrir, sselɛa n yal asɣaṛ i d-yețțaken rriḥa taẓiḍant, leḥwayeǧ akk ineǧṛen s wacciwen n lfil, s wesɣaṛ ɣlayen d wayen yețwaxedmen s nnḥas d wuzzal akk-d eṛxem ;
Tqeṛṛbem ɣer tejmaɛt n wid yextaṛ Ṛebbi d imezwura yesɛan ismawen-nsen uran deg wawal n Ṛebbi. Tqeṛṛbem ɣer lmeṣbeḥ-nni akk-d kra n wid yeznuzun itbiren, wid yețqadaṛen irgazen-nsent akk-d wid ineqqen imawlan-nsen.
Lmelk wis xemsa yewwet lbuq. Yiwet n lḥaǧa annect-ilaț am akken d adrar ameqqran i deg tecɛel tmes yețțuḍeggeṛ ɣer lqaɛa.
Yețmeslay-asen-d akka : Ilaq aț-țɛiwneḍ aț-țeskker ccwal, tura axaṭer ilaq-asen yerwel i ubecceṛ n wawal n Sidi Ṛebbi ; imiren teḥbes-ik , qeblet-eț alamma ț-țaggara, i teṛwiḥin-ik tjem s tezmert-ik.
Akken daɣen ula d iles ; ɣas mecṭuḥ deg yiman-is, yețzuxxu s lecɣal imeqqranen. Walit times tamecṭuḥt i gzemren aț-țesseṛɣ tiẓgi tameqqrant.
M'ara d-yaweḍ wayen innekmalen, ț-țigejdit i k-id-yufan aɛeṛqen. S wakka, yedṛa-d lmeṣbeḥ iwakken kra n win i d-ițeffɣen seg ul-ik, a tent-id-yawi ɣer webrid.
Agellid Lizyas, Quseb n temdint n Antyuc akk-d Meryem-nni iwumi d-kkant tqeddact n Sidna Ɛisa, Ilul di 11th, Luciz, Ilul Nuḥs, Azal n ṛebɛa yiseggasen aya, akk-d weltma-s tameṭṭut n Ilicaba, neḥliḥ-nni iwakken a d-nnejmaɛen ɣer temdint n Biri si tejmaɛt n temdint n Biri.
țțazzalen-d ɣer yiwen umeṛkanti isem-is Akilas akk-d Brisila, wid yețmuqulen s unejmaɛ n ccṛeɛ, ḥeṛsen-t ɣef ddemma n ugellid akk-d tgelda.
Yuɣal issawel i ugellid d tagelda, iwakken aț-țerreḍ lqeddacen-nsen ɣef yidmaren-nsen.
Yiwen wass, ataya yiwen uɛewdiw nniḍen d azeggaɣ am tmes. Win i t-id-irekben, tețțunefk-as tezmert ad ikkes amkan ger ifassen n ugellid.
Lɛeskeṛ n temdint n Filibus wwin-d tiftilin-nni s lexbaṛ n lxiṛ.
