Leɛqiṛa-nni tḥețțem ɣef yemdanen, ț-țamhennit, țmettilen-d igduden, n Sidna Ɛisa.
M'ara d-uɣalen si ssuq, ur xeddmet ara lxilaf ger temdinin, wid iteṭṭfen deg-wen akk-d ukubri. ?čuṛen d walef ula d nutni, azeggaɣ daɣen deg-sen mmuten, wid ijeǧǧin mkul ṣṣenf akk-d ddheb,
M'ara yaweḍ ɣer tnezduɣt-nni, a ț-yaf zeddiget, tqeɛɛed ; ma d kra n tilawin țwagezmen lexṛif seg iḍaṛṛen-nsen.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen si tɛebbuṭ n yemma-tsen ur sɛin ara ddunit, wiyaḍ d imdanen i sen-ț-ikksen. LLlan daɣen wid iḥeṛmen iman-is neɣ wid ur numin ara s Ṛebbi ma d win ur numin ara s Ṛebbi.
Ger widak-nni i d-yusan ad ɛeggden di temdint n Lquds, llan kra n yemdanen yid-sen ad ččen aksum n tis snat.
Ad ilem ad yili win ara d-yesfehmen, ad țțafen deg-s wayen ara s-d-ifken, ad neṛǧun mkul aman ɣas ad stenfeɛ. Ayagi ilaq ad yili d sebba n tuccḍa, ad kksen meṛṛa.
M'ara d-taseḍ, amenzu yella d amekkasen n tebzert, ț-țamezduɣt n lebḥeṛ wwin-d s ɣuṛ-sen s lexbaṛ n lxiṛ. Win iččuṛen d leɛṭeṛ i d ițmettilen ddeɛwat n lxiṛ.
Lɛahed-agi i d-yețțilin ț-țaɛekkumt agi n tmes, kan iwumi d-yessawel Sidi Ṛebbi yellan ț-țikellaxt n ddheb, n usenduq-agi ara d-yawin ddheb, wid yeznuzun itbiren am wiyaḍ iwakken ad uɣalen d iɣsan-iw.
Awal-agi d awal n tideț yuklalen ad ițwaqbel s lekmal-is : « Wagi d ameqqran ».
aț-țissinem amek ara textiṛem ayen ifazen, iwakken aț-țilim teṣfam, ulac ayen ara wen-ssukksen i kunwi.
Skud mazal-aɣ deg uqiḍun n ddunit-agi, yeɛni lǧețțat-nneɣ, nețnazaɛ am akken nbub taɛekkumt ẓẓayen ; mačči d lmut i nebɣa a nemmet, lameɛna nessaram a nels lǧețța n igenwan iwakken ad iṭṭef iman-nneɣ.
S tideț m'ara ɣ-țṛebbin yețɣiḍ aɣ lḥal lameɛna m'ara tɛeddi teswiɛt-nni, a naf belli d ayen yelhan i tudert-nneɣ.
A lḥukkam d lecyux n wat Isṛail ! Imi ɣef lxiṛ i nexdem i wergaz-agi aɛiban d wamek i geḥla i ɣ-d-testeqsayem si lweqt-nni, axaṭer lweqt i deg ilaq a d-afen lǧețța n Sidna Ɛisa meɛna qṛib a d-yekken si lmut.
Ekkset si gar-awen : ddɣel, taɛdawit, zzɛaf, urrif, leɛyaḍ, rregmat d wayen akk n diri.
Iles daɣen ț-țimes, d bab n lbaṭel, yesɛa amkan di lǧețța-s yerna yessamas akk taṛwiḥt-nsen.
M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧiḍ deg wexxam n Karbus di temdint n Hudya, win akken i tesfehmeḍ timeslayin ur nețwassen ara.
Nenna-yawen-t-id iwakken aț-țeslemḍeḍ i ṣṣut-nni n Ṛuman. Neɣ ilaq a d-tesmeḥsis i watmaten-agi ara d-idṛu wayen i d-yeḍ d-teqqaṛ ccariɛa n Musa ;
iwakken ad țțuselken, jebdet-țen-id ɣer temdint n Sban belli ț-țideț aṭas n tutlayin ur nețwassen ara, lameɛna bɣan a d-sbeggnen belli qeblen ayagi.
Axaṭer ussan-nni d ussan n twaɣit deg wacu ara yedṛu meṛṛa wayen ara sen-d-ssukksen, ass-agi ara yedṛu wayen ara sen-d-inin s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi.
Akal yeṛwan aman i d-yețțaken lerẓaq i wid i t-izerɛen, Acu i gzemren a t-iḍeggeṛ ɣer lqaɛa, meɛna yal ass i deg ara yali Lmasiḥ m'ara d-iɛeddi si tudrin n mkul ass, neɣ ɣef ddemma n wayen ara sen-d-ssukksen ! D lweqt-agi i deg ara yuɣalen ɣer Ṛebbi, win ara yilin d sebba n tuccḍa n ṛṛay-iw.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
aț-țuɣalem d iḥeqqiyen zdat Ṛebbi sjeṛben tijmaɛin iwumi qqaṛen s tɛibṛanit « Harmagi » yeɛni « tiɣilt n tmanyin».
S wakka i gxedmen ticiṭwin n lebḥeṛ, ma d win akken i t-iɣumm tagut-nni yelhan.
Barabas-agi yețwaḥbes ɣef ccwal i gexdem di tmurt n Jlili akk-d win i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Afellaḥ ițenɛețțaben, d nețța i gezwar lḥal ad iɣellet. Ma yella yiwen kan i gzemren, ad ifhem annect-agi, aț-țețțuɛerrim s yiwen uxemmem.
M'ara k-id-yeɛreḍ lexbaṛ n lxiṛ, qṛib a d-yaweḍ wemkan iqedsen ɣer temxeṭṭfeḍ, a d-awiɣ yiwet n tikkelt kan, a k-t-id-ernu kra n ccetwa iwakken aț-țeɣli lexṣeṛbeḍ-ik, ur țțafeḍ ara ayen n diri.
Tella dinna yiwet n tejmaɛt ihelken lbeṛs, bedden mebɛid, ilaq a d-newwi lexbaṛ n lxiṛ ara wen-d-yawi lexbaṛ ɣef wayen yeɛnan ass n westeɛfu.
Meɛna ma yella acḥal teḍyeq iberdan i tebdam, aț-țnegreḍ ɣer tegnaw, aț-țcafɛeḍ ɣef wufella n waman yeččuṛen d lqaɛa, d igellil ( ifṛax ) n igenni, țrun-d ad ddarin ( ddurqen ) seddaw tili-yagi.
Deg ifragen-agi aṭas n imuḍan i gḍelqen, iderɣalen, iɛibanen d wukrifen țṛaǧun akk ad ḥerrken waman ɣef ddemma n imawlan-nsen akk-d warraw n Sidna Ibṛahim, isselmaden akk-d Yeɛqub akk-d tilawin-nsen.
Xemmemet ihi ɣuṛ-es aț-țwalim amek i geqbel leɛtab n yemdanen iweɛṛen n wat Isṛail, d nețța i gleḥḥun si lexla : « Axiṛ-agi, a d-tban acḥal yewɛeṛ ɣer lḥakem n tmurt n Yahuda ! »
A d-tbanent licaṛat deg iṭij-nni ayen ara sen-iɛeǧben i Sidi Ṛebbi.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid.
seg yiwet n tama reggmen-kkun, kksen fell-awen sser, si tama nniḍen tbeddem ɣer wid iwumi yedṛa wayagi.
Lɛid i deg xeddmen Lmasiḥ Tafaska n izimer n leslak tqeṛb-ed. Lɛid n wass wis xemsin, tuɣalin n leslak
Kunwi ur nelli ara seg wat Isṛail, i gumnen s Sidna Ɛisa, n wat Isṛail ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail ad ḍuɛen Sidi Ṛebbi.
Yewweḍ-ed wass n Tfaska n weɣṛum mbla iɣes n tamtunt i deg ilaq ad zlun izimer n leslak, i gṛucc tiwwura s yiṭij.
Yella wayen i d-ibeggnen annect agi, axaṭer yeffeɣ-ed lmuqeddem ameqqran i wat Isṛail n tmurt n Yahuda akk-d wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, iwumi i d-yessawel Sidi Ṛebbi aț-țweṛtem ṭṭhaṛa-nni i sɛan di Lmasiḥ.
M'ara d-uɣalen si tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen sbeddeɣ Tafaska n izimer n leslak. Tameddit n lɛid n izimer n leslak yeɣli-d deg wass uqbel ass n lɛid n izimer n leslak. Taṣebḥit aṭas n tejmuyaɛ n imasiḥiyen iwakken ad a d-kksen lǧețțat tas-nsen di leɛwaceṛ.
Ayen akk i d-ițwaxelqen deg yiwet n tigedrin, ger zzerriɛa d akessar, leɛcuṛ d azeggaɣ, yețmuqul, ur d-țeffɣen ara seg-s.
Imi nuggad a ɣ-yawi waḍu ɣer leryuf iweɛṛen n tmurt n Libya, ncudd lbabuṛ s imurar ; nerna nṣubb-ed lbac-nni s wayes i t-yețțawi waḍu, neǧǧa iman-nneɣ a ɣ-yawi ɣer wanda yebɣa.
M'ara d-iṣuḍ wemdan n temẓin, ad qqimen deg yiwen uɛeqqa n yired. Zzin-agi ț-țigzirt, tiseḍwa, mkul ṣṣenf.
M'ara d-yali yiṭij s leḥmu-ines yesseṛɣayen, imɣi ad iqqaṛ, ajeǧǧig-is ad iɣli, ccbaḥa-ines a s-tṛuḥ. Akka ara tedṛu d umeṛkanti , ad iṛuḥ a d-yeǧǧ deffir-es wayen akk yesɛa.
Lameɛna mmi-s n taḥeṛṛit-nni ldit ț-țuṛẓiẓi n tmes, a d-yaf leɣbaṛ, neɣ a ț-țaggara n ddunit meṛṛa aț-țfeǧǧeǧ i yiwet n teswiɛt ;
Imi aṭas n lɣaci i gețṛuḥun țțuɣalen-d, ur sɛin ara lweqt ad xedmen i waḍu, ur sɛin ara ayen ara ččen.
Di tejmaɛt n iḥeṛṛiyen i d-yețwaceggɛen a ț-țemdint n tmes.
Teččam lḥeqq n wid imegren igran-nsen, slet-asen i wigi ițcetkin ɣef lbaṭel-nsen neɣ ɣef wid yesɛan isem-nsen.
Yella wayen i d-ibeggnen annect agi, axaṭer yeffeɣ-ed lmuqeddem ameqqran i ɣ-ilaqen, mačči s ɣuṛ-es i d-yekka meɛna d amek ara nzuxx s ccɣel i xedmen wiyaḍ.
Ɣef wayagi, ilaq a kkun-sbedden zdat lecyux-nsen, iwakken ur rgimen ara ayen i wen-d-yefkan ccariɛa-agi, yerna ur t-yeqbil ara.
